      <h4 class="how__t">What Is a Time Zone?</h4>
      <p class="how__p">
        A time zone is a region of the earth where all the clocks are set to the same time. This is done for two purposes: to ensure
        that “noon” doesn’t occur in the middle of the night, and to support legal/business/social needs for those in the
        same time zone.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="learn__right">
      <img class="learn__image" src="{{relative_path}}images/learn-earth.jpg" alt="PublicNTP Earth">
    </div>
