      <h4 class="how__t">Daylight Saving Time</h4>
      <p class="how__p">
        Several parts of the world, primarily North America and Europe, advance the clocks during summer (typically one hour, though
        exceptions do exist). The original proponents for daylight saving time claimed a number of projected benefits from
        increasing the number of evening hours with daylight during the summer months.
      </p>
